attributes.review: I want to start by complimenting our wonderful president. He has done so much for our country. Like literally. Can you guys believe it? This man deserves a dog treat. I just want to warn some of you that this is a very dangerous app. It has caused me to throw up because of seeing a certain person. I legit had to go to the hospital and take a chill pill because my beautiful eyes were poisoned by the person’s ugliness. Wait. Actually, let me tell you a story of how this app almost killed my dog. I was walking my dog. His name is Max, by the way. We were at a park when suddenly my phone buzzed so loudly. I had so, so many notifications from this app. Like at most, 2000. But the strange thing was the numbers kept rising and rising. I couldn’t take the noisiness anymore so I turned my phone on do not disturb. What happened next almost blew my head off. Wait. Let me get a drink. I deserve some water right now. Actually, I’m tired. Goodnight.
attributes.title: Technical difficultly. MUST READ❤️
